stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending
    pending --> claimed: runner claims
    pending --> canceled: user cancels
    claimed --> running: running
    claimed --> failed: failed / timeout
    claimed --> canceled: user cancels
    running --> completed: completed
    running --> failed: failed / timeout
    running --> canceled: cancel / hard timeout
    failed --> completed: results recovered
    completed --> processed: results parsed
    processed --> [*]
    canceled --> [*]
